properties.query:
SELECT 
"Transaction_ID" as "order_id", 
"Transaction_Date" as "date",
"Purchase_Amount" as "payment",
"Product_Category" as "category",
"Country" as "country"
FROM FLOWFILE

properties.query:
SELECT 
"order_id", 
"customer_id",
SUBSTRING("order_purchase_timestamp", 1, 10) as "date",
"order_status" as "status",
'-' as "payment",
'-' as "country"
FROM FLOWFILE
WHERE "order_status" = 'delivered'
